rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div class="enrleftcell" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 393.25px; min-height: 1px; padding-top: 4px; padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; float: left; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; border-right: 2px solid rgb(255, 255, 255);"><label for="mainContent_addonPrompt" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; width: auto; margin-top: 7px;">Add-on Prompt:</label></div><div class="enrrightcell" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1164.02px; min-height: 1px; padding: 4px 5px 3px; float: left; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-left: -2px;"><textarea name="ctl00$mainContent$addonPrompt" rows="3" cols="20" id="mainContent_addonPrompt" class="enrform-control" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); overflow: auto; padding: 5px 10px; background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 3px; width: 800px; max-width: 800px; display: block; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075) 0px 1px 1px inset; transition: border-color 0.15s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.15s ease-in-out; height: auto;"></textarea></div></div><div class="enrrow" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-top: 2px solid rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div class="enrleftcell" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 393.25px; min-height: 1px; padding-top: 4px; padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; float: left; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; border-right: 2px solid rgb(255, 255, 255);"><label for="bsmSelectbsmContainer0" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; width: auto; margin-top: 7px;">Add-ons:</label></div><div class="enrrightcell" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1164.02px; min-height: 1px; padding: 4px 5px 3px; float: left; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-left: -2px;"><div class="bsmContainer" id="bsmContainer0" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><select class="bsmSelect" id="bsmSelectbsmContainer0" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; border-radius: 4px; padding: 6px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255) !important; border: 1px solid rgb(213, 213, 213); display: inline; width: 800px; max-width: 800px;"><option value="" selected="selected" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Click to Select</option><option value="8174" style="box-sizing: border-box;">ARC-BK-BLS - /Class_Images/ARC-BLS-book.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;LS Participant’s Manual&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Includes all foundational concepts covered in the American Red Cross BLS course.&lt;br&gt; Emergency care components covered for adult, child and infant patients include recognition and care for patients experiencing respiratory arrest, cardiac arrest, airway obstruction and opioid overdose.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $30.05</option><option value="14361" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-BK-BLS (12) - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;( 12 ) BLS Provider Manual &lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1102.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;<span> </span> &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;The BLS Provider Manual contains all the information students need to successfully complete the BLS Course. This manual is designed for a single user, with text that is ideal for use as a reference tool before and after the BLS Course. &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $240.00</option><option value="14363" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-EBK-BLS (12) - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;( 12 ) BLS Provider Manual eBook&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-2803.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;<span> </span> &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;The BLS Provider Manual eBook is the electronic equivalent of the AHA’s BLS Provider Manual. It offers an alternative to the printed manual and contains all the information students need to successfully complete the BLS Course.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $180.00</option><option value="14402" class="bsmOptionDisabled" disabled="disabled" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); display: block;">MANUAL: OTHER SOURCE - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;"&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>&lt;strong&gt;Manual: Other Source&lt;/strong&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/THUP.png" width="75" style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span> <span> </span>&lt;i&gt;I already have access to the required AHA manual from a friend, employer, or previous course. I understand it's required before, during, and after class to validate certification.&lt;/i&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; - $0.00</option><option value="14403" class="bsmOptionDisabled" disabled="disabled" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); display: block;">MANUAL: AHA BOOKSTORE - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style="font-size:14px; line-height:1.5; overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:10px;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Buy from AHA.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/_AHA.png" width="55" style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="color:#828282; margin:0;"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Visit &lt;a href="https://ebooks.heart.org" target="_blank"&gt;ebooks.heart.org&lt;/a&gt;(not a 910CPR store) and search your course title (e.g., “BLS Provider Manual”).&lt;/i&gt;No fees from 910CPR. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt; - $0.00</option><option value="8354" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-DVD-INSTR-BLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1105.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA BLS DVD Set&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;DVD set for BLS Instructors to teach the BLS Course, the BLS Renewal Course, and for skills practice/ testing sessions for HeartCode® BLS.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $108.15</option><option value="8896" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-DVD-INSTR-HS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1123.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® First Aid CPR AED DVD Set&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;DVD courses provide students the highest quality training in the lifesaving skills of first aid and/or CPR and use of an AED&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/P&gt; - $210.00</option><option value="11622" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-DIGVID-INSTR-BLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1414.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA BLS Course Digital Video&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Digital version of the BLS DVD Set for BLS Instructors to teach the BLS Course, the BLS Renewal Course, and for skills practice/ testing sessions for HeartCode® BLS. Videos can be streamed online with an internet connection or downloaded on up to 3 devices.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $99.90</option><option value="7246" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-EBK-ACLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-3100.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;""&gt;HA ACLS Provider Manual eBook&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Electronic ACLS Provider Manual. Teaches cardiac arrest prevention, high-performance teams, CPR, acute dysrhythmias, stroke, ACS, and post-cardiac arrest care. &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $46.38</option><option value="13067" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-EBK-INSTR-ACLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-3101.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA ACLS Instructor Manual eBook - $61.80</option><option value="9729" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-EBK-INSTR-BLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-3103.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA BLS Instructor Manual eBook&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;The electronic equivalent to the BLS Instructor Manual, which provides information for teaching both the Instructor-led training (ILT) and blended-learning options for the BLS Provider Course&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $47.05</option><option value="8895" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-EBK-INSTR-HS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/2