loat:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;SHA 10 Hr | General Industry | Spanish&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt; (Not Valid in New York City)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $75.00</option><option value="14000" style="box-sizing: border-box;">OSHA-OLT-30CONSTREN - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;O&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/EC-OSHA30CON.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;SHA 30 Hr | Construction | English&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt; (Not Valid in New York City)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $150.00</option><option value="14001" style="box-sizing: border-box;">OSHA-OLT-30CONSTRSP - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;O&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/EC-OSHA30CONSP.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;SHA 30 Hr | Construction | Spanish&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt; (Not Valid in New York City)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $150.00</option><option value="14002" style="box-sizing: border-box;">OSHA-OLT-30GENINEN - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;O&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/EC-OSHA30GEN.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;SHA 30 Hr | General Industry | English&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt; (Not Valid in New York City)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $150.00</option><option value="14003" style="box-sizing: border-box;">OSHA-OLT-30GENINSP - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;O&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/EC-OSHA30GENSP.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;SHA 30 Hr | General Industry | Spanish&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt; (Not Valid in New York City)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $150.00</option><option value="7197" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-BK-PALS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;P&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1119.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;ALS Provider Manual&lt;br&gt;<span> </span> &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt; The AHA PALS Provider Manual contains all the information students need to successfully complete the AHA PALS Course. The PALS Provider Manual is for use by a single student and provides information needed before, during, and after class.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $76.68</option><option value="7199" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-EBK-PALS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;P&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-2812.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;ALS Provider Manual eBook&lt;br&gt;<span> </span> &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Contains all of the information students need to know to successfully complete the PALS Course and is designed for use by a single user as a student reference tool pre- and post-course. It is also used as a clinical reference. &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $55.00</option><option value="9257" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-2020PRE-PALS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;PALS Precourse Self-Assessment and Precourse Work&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/kj-1487.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Precourse Work: Students review content via online videos, covering medical subjects, before class, allowing more time for hands-on skills training.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt; Students must score at least 70% and bring the completion certificate to class.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $0.00</option><option value="7995" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC+SKILLS-PALS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;PALS Renew<span> </span> [AHA]&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Includes Online PALS HeartCode &amp; Skills Test Appointment&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $268.00</option><option value="8405" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-SKILLS-PALS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;PALS Skills Session &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;(Student-provided Heartcode)&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $100.00</option><option value="11304" style="box-sizing: border-box;">STB-OLT+SKILLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;STOP THE BLEED® Skills testing - $22.00</option><option value="7537" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-BBP - &lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/15-1405.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;Heartsaver® Bloodborne Pathogens Online&lt;br&gt;<span> </span> &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Learn to protect against exposure to blood or blood-containing materials. Pair with site-specific instruction to meet OSHA requirements for bloodborne pathogens.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;No in-person element to this course.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $23.32</option><option value="8563" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-HS_FA - &lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1402.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;Heartsaver® First Aid Online&lt;br&gt;<span> </span> &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Teaches students the essential knowledge for providing basic first aid in various scenarios. Ideal for those seeking general first aid skills.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $18.50</option><option value="7198" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ILT-BLS - &lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/ILT.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;BLS In-Person Instructor-led Renewal [AHA] &lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Add an in-person BLS renewal.<span> </span> Completed during PALS/ACLS/ASLS skills testing date/time.<span> </span> Receive a BLS certification card that matches your advanced cert's expiration date. &lt;b&gt;No online coursework required prior to class date.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $67.00</option><option value="14570" style="box-sizing: border-box;">HSI-ILT-FACPRAED-USCG - &lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/HSINST-203.png" width="75" style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt; Are you taking this class to meet your USCG Captain's License &lt;i&gt;Elementary First Aid and CPR&lt;/i&gt; requirement?&lt;br&gt; &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>Choose 'YES' for &lt;br&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>&lt;b&gt;"HSI Adult First Aid | CPR AED"&lt;/b&gt; (above),&lt;br&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>and check here to receive a &lt;b&gt;HSINST-203 Recognition of Participation&lt;/b&gt; document with your eCard. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $0.00</option><option value="15084" style="box-sizing: border-box;">2025 ACLS INSTRUCTOR UPDATE - 2025 ACLS Instructor Update - $0.00</option><option value="15081" style="box-sizing: border-box;">2025_BLS_INSTRUCTOR _UPDATE - 2025 BLS Instructor Update - $0.00</option><option value="15082" style="box-sizing: border-box;">2025_HEARTSAVER_INSTRUCTOR_UPDATE - 2025 Heartsaver® Instructor Update - $0.00</option><option value="15083" style="box-sizing: border-box;">2025_PALS_INSTRUCTOR_UPDATE - 2025 PALS Instructor Update - $0.00</option><option value="12249" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-PALS+:CHD - A&lt;IMG SRC="https://d32pa7zymd21yl.cloudfront.net/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/646ce19b0765b2911af0b3b6072b6de6/2/0/20-1444_pals_plus_congen_heart_disease_1.png" WIDTH="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS PLUS™: Congenital Heart Disease (CHD): &lt;BR&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;P STYLE="COLOR: #828282"&gt;&lt;I&gt;1.00 HOUR ONLINE, 0.5 POSSIBLE CE&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;BR&gt; - $22.00</option><option value="11287" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-PALS+:POSTARREST - A&lt;img src="https://d32pa7zymd21yl.cloudfront.net/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/8fce8601fc2f12d655469c75674153c0/2/0/20-1445_pals_plus_post_card_arrest_care.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS Plus™: Post-Cardiac Arrest Care Module&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;1.00 Hour Online, 0.5 Possible CE&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $22.00</option><option value="11456" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-PALS+:ULTRASOUND - A&lt;img src="https://d32pa7zymd21yl.cloudfront.net/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/8fce8601fc2f12d655469c75674153c0/2/0/20-1446_pals_plus_ultrasound.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS Plus™: Ultrasound Module&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;1.00 Hour Online, 1.25 Possible CE&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $22.00</option><option value="11285" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-PALS+:SEDATION - A&lt;img src="https://d32pa7zymd21yl.cloudfront.net/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/8fce8601fc2f12d655469c75674153c0/2/0/20-1447_pals_plus_sedation_analgesia.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS Plus™: Sedation &amp; Analgesia Module&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;1.00 Hour Online, 0.25 Possible CE&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $22.00</option><option value="11286" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-PALS+:TECH - A&lt;img src="https://d32pa7zymd21yl.cloudfront.net/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/8fce8601fc2f12d655469c75674153c0/2/0/20-1448_pals_plus_tech_dep_child.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS Plus™: Technology-Dependent Child Module&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;1.00 Hour Online, 0.25 Possible CE&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $22.00</option><option value="11283" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-PALS+:ABUSE - A&lt;img src="https://d32pa7zymd21yl.cloudfront.net/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/8fce8601fc2f12d655469c75674153c0/2/0/20-1449_pals_plus_toxicology.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS Plus™: Child Abuse Module&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;1.00 Hour Online, 0.25 Possible CE&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $22.00</option><option value="11457" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-PALS+:TRAUMA - A&lt;img src="https://d32pa7zymd21yl.cloudfront.net/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/8fce8601fc2f12d655469c75674153c0/2/0/20-1449_pals_plus_toxicology.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS Plus™: Trauma Module&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;1.00 Hour Online, 1.00 Possible CE&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $22.00</option><option value="11282" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-PALS+:TOX - A&lt;img src="https://d32pa7zymd21yl.cloudfront.net/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/8fce8601fc2f12d655469c75674153c0/2/0/20-1450_pals_plus_child_absue.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS Plus™: Toxicology Module&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;1.00 Hour Online, 0.75 Possible CE&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $22.00</option><option value="11284" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-PALS+:AIRWAY - A&lt;img src="https://d32pa7zymd21yl.cloudfront.net/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/8fce8601fc2f12d655469c75674153c0/2/0/20-1451_pals_plus_adv_airway.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS Plus™: Airway Management Module&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;1.00 Hour Online, 0.5 Possible CE&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $22.00</option><option value="9668" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ILT-INSTR-ACLS - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/acls______.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;CLS - Instructor [American Heart Association] &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; - $300.00</option><option value="14245" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ILT-INSTR-BLS - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/bls______.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;bLS - Instructor [American Heart Association] &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; - $300.00</option><option value="11288" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-BP - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/15-1425.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Achieving Accuracy: BP Measurement eLearning Course&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Improve your blood pressure measurement skills with the new Achieving Accuracy: BP Measurement e-Learning module co-developed by the AHA and AMA.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt; - $26.50</option><option value="7536" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-HS_CPRAED - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1401.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® CPR AED Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;eLearning portion of the Heartsaver CPR AED blended learning course, designed to teach students the cognitive information needed for CPR training and how to use an AED&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $30.00</option><option value="7540" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-HS_FACPRAED-PEDI - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1404.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® Pediatric First Aid CPR AED Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;eLearning portion of the Heartsaver Pediatric First Aid CPR AED blended learning course, designed to teach students the cognitive information needed for pediatric first aid, CPR, and AED training&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $40.00</option><option value="12055" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-INSTR-PALS-ESSENTIALS - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1417.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS Instructor Essentials Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Self-directed, online portion of the PALS Instructor Essentials blended learning course covering the steps for becoming an AHA Instructor and steps of the instruction cycle&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/P&gt; - $41.20</option><option value="8894" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-INSTR-HS-ESSENTIALS - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1418.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® Instructor Essentials Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Self-directed, online portion of the Heartsaver Instructor Essentials blended learning course covering steps for becoming an AHA Instructor and steps of the instruction cycle&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/P&gt; - $40.00</option><option value="9660" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-INSTR-ACLS-ESSENTIALS - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1419.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA ACLS Instructor Essentials Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Self-directed, online portion of the ACLS Instructor Essentials blended learning Course covering steps for becoming an AHA ACLS Instructor and steps of the instruction cycle.&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/P&gt; - $40.00</option><option value="7539" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-HS_FACPRAED-B - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1440.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® Basic - First Aid CPR AED Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Basic course focuses on core curriculum for providing first aid, CPR, and using an AED effectively. Covers basics of recognizing and administering first aid for common emergencies. &lt;b&gt;Not OSHA-compliant.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $40.00</option><option value="11335" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-HS_FACPRAED-T - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1440.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® Total - First Aid CPR AED Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;eLearning portion of the Heartsaver Total® First Aid CPR AED course. Teaches the cognitive information needed for first aid, CPR, and AED training.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Completing all elements results in a course completion card designed to meet OSHA requirements.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $40.00</option><option value="14049" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-HS_FACPRAED-T-95 - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1440.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® Total - First Aid CPR AED Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;eLearning portion of the Heartsaver Total® First Aid CPR AED course. Teaches the cognitive information needed for first aid, CPR, and AED training.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Completing all elements results in a course completion card designed to meet OSHA requirements.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $95.00</option><option value="7276" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-BLS - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-3553.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA BLS Provider HeartCode® &lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Use this option if you need a code for the online program.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $37.00</option><option value="7864" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-ACLS - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-3554.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA HeartCode® ACLS Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Online portion of ACLS blended learning that will prepare students for hands-on skills session with an AHA ACLS Instructor or on a simulation station.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you have already been issued a HeartCode from your employer or school, select 'No' here.&lt;b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $185.00</option><option value="9662" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ILT-ACLS - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/ILT.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;CLS In-person Instructor-led Renewal&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Builds on BLS skills, emphasizing high-quality CPR, emergency interventions, team dynamics, algorithms, post-cardiac-arrest care, airway management, and pharmacology. Add in-person ACLS renewal during PALS skills testing.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pre-test Reqired&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $225.00</option><option value="8900" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ILT-HS_FA - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/ILT.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® First Aid - $50.00</option><option value="13620" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-ASLS/INHOSPITAL - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/In.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA ASLS Online: In-Hospital Provider&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Online portion of ASLS blended learning that will prepare students for hands-on skills session with an AHA Instructor.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you have already been issued a HeartCode from your employer or school, select 'No' here.&lt;b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $186.77</option><option value="13619" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-ASLS/PREHOSPITAL - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/Pre.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA ASLS Online: Prehospital Provider&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Online portion of ASLS blended learning that will prepare students for hands-on skills session with an AHA Instructor.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you have already been issued a HeartCode from your employer or school, select 'No' here.&lt;b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $186.77</option><option value="13621" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-ASLS/ALL - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/PreIn.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA ASLS Online: Prehospital &amp; In-Hospital Provider&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Online portion of ASLS blended learning that will prepare students for hands-on skills session with an AHA Instructor.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you have already been issued a HeartCode from your employer or school, select 'No' here.&lt;b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $185.00</option><option value="8399" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ILT-HS_FACPRAED-USCG - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/JohnsHSFACPRAED.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;re you taking this class to meet your USCG Captain's License &lt;i&gt;Elementary First Aid and CPR&lt;/i&gt; requirement?&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;br&gt;Choose 'YES' for&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;"Heartsaver® First Aid with CPR/AED - TOTAL"&lt;/b&gt; (above)&lt;br&gt;AND here to receive an AMERHA-216 with your eCard.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $0.00</option><option value="14233" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ILT-INSTR-PALS - AHA - PALS - Become an American Heart Association Instructor &lt;div style="overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 5px;"&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/_AHA.png" alt="AHA Logo" style="width:25px; float:left; margin-right:5px;"&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/Ippin.png" alt="PALS Instructor Icon" style="float:right; width:100px; vertical-align:top;"&gt; &lt;/div&gt; - $300.00</option><option value="15436" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-INSTR-BLS-ESSENTIALS - BLS Instructor Essentials Online - $40.00</option><option value="12333" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-HS_FACPRAED-K12 - Heartsaver First Aid CPR AED for K-12 School - $0.00</option><option value="8189" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-INSTR-BLS-CODE1 - Heartsaver® Instructor Essentials / Monitoring / Virtual Live &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; - $150.00</option><option value="7975" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-PALS - PALS HeartCode® [AHA]<span> </span> &lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Use this option if you need a code for the online program.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $186.77</option><option value="13725" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ILT-PALS - PALS In-person Instructor-led Renewal - $225.00</option></select><ol id="bsmListbsmContainer0" class="bsmList" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0px; position: relative; display: block; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none; max-width: 800px;"><li class="bsmListItem" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none; background: rgb(221, 221, 221); border: 1px solid rgb(187, 187, 187); width: auto; margin: 0px 0px -1px; line-height: 1em; display: list-item;"><span class="bsmListItemLabel" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; display: block;">MANUAL: OTHER SOURCE - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;"&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Manual: Other Source&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/THUP.png" width="75" style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt; &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt; &lt;i&gt;I already have access to the required AHA manual from a friend, employer, or previous course. I understand it's required before, during, and after class to validate certification.&lt;/i&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; - $0.00</span><a href="https://www.enrollware.com/admin/course-edit.aspx?ret=course-list.aspx&amp;id=344085#" class="bsmListItemRemove" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(187, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.12s ease-out; position: absolute; right: 0px; top: 0px; padding: 5px;">remove</a></li><li class="bsmListItem" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none; background: rgb(221, 221, 221); border: 1px solid rgb(187, 187, 187); width: auto; margin: 0px 0px -1px; line-height: 1em; display: list-item;"><span class="bsmListItemLabel" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; display: block;">MANUAL: AHA BOOKSTORE - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style="font-size:14px; line-height:1.5; overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:10px;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Buy from AHA.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/_AHA.png" width="55" style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="color:#828282; margin:0;"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Visit &lt;a href="https://ebooks.heart.org" target="_blank"&gt;ebooks.heart.org&lt;/a&gt;(not a 910CPR store) and search your course title (e.g., “BLS Provider Manual”).&lt;/i&gt;No fees from 910CPR. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt; - $0.00</span><a href="https://www.enrollware.com/admin/course-edit.aspx?ret=course-list.aspx&amp;id=344085#" class="bsmListItemRemove" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(187, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.12s ease-out; position: absolute; right: 0px; top: 0px; padding: 5px;">remove</a></li></ol><select size="4" name="ctl00$mainContent$addonList" multiple="multiple" id="mainContent_addonList" title="Click to Select" class="enrform-control" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; border-radius: 3px; padding: 5px 10px; background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); height: auto; display: none; width: 100%; max-width: 800px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075) 0px 1px 1px inset; transition: border-color 0.15s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.15s ease-in-out;"><span> </span>	<option value="8174" style="box-sizing: border-box;">ARC-BK-BLS - /Class_Images/ARC-BLS-book.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;LS Participant’s Manual&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Includes all foundational concepts covered in the American Red Cross BLS course.&lt;br&gt; Emergency care components covered for adult, child and infant patients include recognition and care for patients experiencing respiratory arrest, cardiac arrest, airway obstruction and opioid overdose.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $30.05</option><span> </span>	<option value="14361" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-BK-BLS (12) - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;( 12 ) BLS Provider Manual &lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1102.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;<span> </span> &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;The BLS Provider Manual contains all the information students need to successfully complete the BLS Course. This manual is designed for a single user, with text that is ideal for use as a reference tool before and after the BLS Course. &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $240.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="14363" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-EBK-BLS (12) - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;( 12 ) BLS Provider Manual eBook&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-2803.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;<span> </span> &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;The BLS Provider Manual eBook is the electronic equivalent of the AHA’s BLS Provider Manual. It offers an alternative to the printed manual and contains all the information students need to successfully complete the BLS Course.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $180.00</option><span> </span>	<option selected="selected" value="14402" style="box-sizing: border-box;">MANUAL: OTHER SOURCE - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;"&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>&lt;strong&gt;Manual: Other Source&lt;/strong&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/THUP.png" width="75" style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span> <span> </span>&lt;i&gt;I already have access to the required AHA manual from a friend, employer, or previous course. I understand it's required before, during, and after class to validate certification.&lt;/i&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; - $0.00</option><span> </span>	<option selected="selected" value="14403" style="box-sizing: border-box;">MANUAL: AHA BOOKSTORE - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style="font-size:14px; line-height:1.5; overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:10px;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Buy from AHA.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/_AHA.png" width="55" style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="color:#828282; margin:0;"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Visit &lt;a href="https://ebooks.heart.org" target="_blank"&gt;ebooks.heart.org&lt;/a&gt;(not a 910CPR store) and search your course title (e.g., “BLS Provider Manual”).&lt;/i&gt;No fees from 910CPR. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt; - $0.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="8354" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-DVD-INSTR-BLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1105.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA BLS DVD Set&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;DVD set for BLS Instructors to teach the BLS Course, the BLS Renewal Course, and for skills practice/ testing sessions for HeartCode® BLS.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $108.15</option><span> </span>	<option value="8896" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-DVD-INSTR-HS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1123.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® First Aid CPR AED DVD Set&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;DVD courses provide students the highest quality training in the lifesaving skills of first aid and/or CPR and use of an AED&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/P&gt; - $210.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="11622" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-DIGVID-INSTR-BLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1414.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA BLS Course Digital Video&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Digital version of the BLS DVD Set for BLS Instructors to teach the BLS Course, the BLS Renewal Course, and for skills practice/ testing sessions for HeartCode® BLS. Videos can be streamed online with an internet connection or downloaded on up to 3 devices.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $99.90</option><span> </span>	<option value="7246" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-EBK-ACLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-3100.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;""&gt;HA ACLS Provider Manual eBook&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Electronic ACLS Provider Manual. Teaches cardiac arrest prevention, high-performance teams, CPR, acute dysrhythmias, stroke, ACS, and post-cardiac arrest care. &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $46.38</option><span> </span>	<option value="13067" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-EBK-INSTR-ACLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-3101.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA ACLS Instructor Manual eBook - $61.80</option><span> </span>	<option value="9729" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-EBK-INSTR-BLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-3103.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA BLS Instructor Manual eBook&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;The electronic equivalent to the BLS Instructor Manual, which provides information for teaching both the Instructor-led training (ILT) and blended-learning options for the BLS Provider Course&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $47.05</option><span> </span>	<option value="8895" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-EBK-INSTR-HS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-3114.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® Instructor First Aid CPR AED Manual eBook &lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Instructor manual for Heartsaver Instructors to provide students the highest quality training in the lifesaving skills of first aid and/or CPR and use of an AED&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/P&gt; - $59.25</option><span> </span>	<option value="10492" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-EBK-HS_FACPRAED - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-3117.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® First Aid CPR AED Student eBook - $3.71</option><span> </span>	<option value="8311" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-EBK-HS_FACPRAED-ESP - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-3138.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® First Aid CPR AED Student eBook - Spanish - $3.71</option><span> </span>	<option value="7538" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-SKILLS-HS_FA - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/BL.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® First Aid<span> </span> [AHA]&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Commonly for Rec Therapy majors.<span> </span> Verify with your school.. &lt;/i&gt; - $50.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="7996" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC+SKILLS-ACLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/BL.png" width="75" style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;CLS Renew Online [AHA]&lt;br&gt; &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Includes online portion of ACLS blended learning and the hands-on skills session with an AHA ACLS Instructor.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $264.14</option><span> </span>	<option value="8406" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-SKILLS-ACLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/BLSS.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;CLS Skills Session Only&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;(Student-provided Heartcode)&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Use this option if you have already purchased/completed an AHA ACLS HeartCode&lt;b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $85.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="11806" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-SKILLS-HS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/BLSS.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA First Aid Skills Testing - $30.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="13448" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ETEST-PALS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/kj-1489.PNG" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS Exam for PALS Providers&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;The PALS online exam measures cognitive knowledge from the PALS Course. Administered by the instructor, it consists of 50 multiple-choice questions, taking 45-60 minutes to complete. Must be taken in one sitting. Two attempts allowed. A score of 84%+ is required to pass.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $0.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="9661" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-BK-INSTR-ACLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;ACLS Instructor Manual &lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1107.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Provides lesson plans and information for teaching the ACLS Course on an initial or update basis, including classroom-based and blended-learning options.&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/P&gt; - $68.79</option><span> </span>	<option value="9254" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-2025PRE-ACLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;ACLS Precourse Self-Assessment and Precourse Work &lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/kj-1498.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Online video lessons and self-assessment tool for students to prepare for their ACLS course.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $0.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="7974" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-BK-ACLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;ACLS Provider Student Manual&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1106.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;""&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;The ACLS Provider Manual contains all of the information students need to know to successfully complete the ACLS Course. The ACLS Provider Manual is a student reference tool pre-and post-course. It is also used as a clinical reference.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $66.13</option><span> </span>	<option value="13434" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-INSTR-RENEWAL-ACLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;AHA ACLS Instructor Renewal - $0.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="10401" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ECARD-BLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;AHA BLS eCard - $8.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="13444" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-INSTR-RENEWAL-BLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;AHA BLS Instructor Renewal - $0.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="14391" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ECARD-HS_CPRAED - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;AHA Heartsaver CPR/ AED eCard<span> </span> &lt;b&gt;(Optional)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Upon successful completion of this course, students are eligible to for a 2-year, American Heart Association Heartsaver Completion card. &lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;AHA eCard fees are not covered by the host organization.&lt;/b&gt; &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $30.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="11721" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ECARD-HS_FACPRAED 🚒 - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;AHA Heartsaver First Aid/ CPR/ AED eCard 🚒<span> </span> &lt;b&gt;(Optional)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Upon successful completion of this course, students are eligible to for a 2-year, American Heart Association Heartsaver Completion card. &lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;AHA eCard fees are not covered by the host organization.&lt;/b&gt; &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $30.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="11517" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ECARD-HS_FACPRAED - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;AHA Heartsaver First Aid/ CPR/ AED eCard<span> </span> &lt;b&gt;(Optional)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Upon successful completion of this course, students are eligible to for a 2-year, American Heart Association Heartsaver Completion card. &lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;AHA eCard fees are not covered by the host organization.&lt;/b&gt; &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $30.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="12788" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ECARD-HS_K-12 🚌 - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;AHA Heartsaver K-12 eCard 🚌 - $12.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="14244" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-EBK-INSTR-PALS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;AHA PALS Instructor Manual eBook - $61.80</option><span> </span>	<option value="7200" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-EBK-BLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;B&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-2803.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;LS Provider Manual eBook&lt;br&gt;<span> </span> &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;The BLS Provider Manual eBook is the electronic equivalent of the AHA’s BLS Provider Manual. It offers an alternative to the printed manual and contains all the information students need to successfully complete the BLS Course.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $17.49</option><span> </span>	<option value="11359" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-SKILLS-BLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;B&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/BLSS.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;LS Skills Session<span> </span> &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;If you have been provided a HeartCode online course from employer or school, choose 'No' here.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $55.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="8352" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-BK-INSTR-BLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;BLS Instructor Manual &lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1103.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Provides information for teaching both the Instructor-led training (ILT) and blended-learning options for the BLS Provider Course&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/P&gt; - $49.75</option><span> </span>	<option value="7973" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-BK-BLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;BLS Provider Student Manual&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1102.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;<span> </span> &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;The BLS Provider Manual contains all the information students need to successfully complete the BLS Course. This manual is designed for a single user, with text that is ideal for use as a reference tool before and after the BLS Course. &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $31.23</option><span> </span>	<option value="8484" style="box-sizing: border-box;">CALL ME - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Call me back with more info!&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/callme.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt; - $0.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="8361" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-BK-HS_FACPRAED - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Heartsaver® First Aid CPR AED Student Workbook&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1126.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt; - $5.50</option><span> </span>	<option value="8249" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-BK-HS_FACPRAED-PEDI - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Heartsaver® Pediatric First Aid CPR AED Student Workbook&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1124.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt; - $3.71</option><span> </span>	<option value="8353" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-INSTR-MONITOR - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Instructor Candidate Monitoring - $50.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="13999" style="box-sizing: border-box;">OSHA-OLT-10CONSTREN - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;O&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/EC-OSHA10CON.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;SHA 10 Hr | Construction | Engilsh&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt; (Not Valid in New York City)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $75.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="13997" style="box-sizing: border-box;">OSHA-OLT-10CONSTRSP - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;O&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/EC-OSHA10CONSP.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;SHA 10 Hr | Construction | Spanish&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt; (Not Valid in New York City)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $75.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="13996" style="box-sizing: border-box;">OSHA-OLT-10GENINEN - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;O&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/EC-OSHA10GEN.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;SHA 10 Hr | General Industry | English&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt; (Not Valid in New York City)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $75.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="13998" style="box-sizing: border-box;">OSHA-OLT-10GENINSP - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;O&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/EC-OSHA10GENSP.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;SHA 10 Hr | General Industry | Spanish&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt; (Not Valid in New York City)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $75.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="14000" style="box-sizing: border-box;">OSHA-OLT-30CONSTREN - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;O&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/EC-OSHA30CON.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;SHA 30 Hr | Construction | English&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt; (Not Valid in New York City)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $150.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="14001" style="box-sizing: border-box;">OSHA-OLT-30CONSTRSP - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;O&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/EC-OSHA30CONSP.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;SHA 30 Hr | Construction | Spanish&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt; (Not Valid in New York City)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $150.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="14002" style="box-sizing: border-box;">OSHA-OLT-30GENINEN - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;O&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/EC-OSHA30GEN.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;SHA 30 Hr | General Industry | English&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt; (Not Valid in New York City)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $150.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="14003" style="box-sizing: border-box;">OSHA-OLT-30GENINSP - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;O&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/EC-OSHA30GENSP.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;SHA 30 Hr | General Industry | Spanish&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt; (Not Valid in New York City)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $150.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="7197" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-BK-PALS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;P&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1119.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;ALS Provider Manual&lt;br&gt;<span> </span> &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt; The AHA PALS Provider Manual contains all the information students need to successfully complete the AHA PALS Course. The PALS Provider Manual is for use by a single student and provides information needed before, during, and after class.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $76.68</option><span> </span>	<option value="7199" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-EBK-PALS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;P&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-2812.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;ALS Provider Manual eBook&lt;br&gt;<span> </span> &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Contains all of the information students need to know to successfully complete the PALS Course and is designed for use by a single user as a student reference tool pre- and post-course. It is also used as a clinical reference. &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $55.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="9257" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-2020PRE-PALS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;PALS Precourse Self-Assessment and Precourse Work&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/kj-1487.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Precourse Work: Students review content via online videos, covering medical subjects, before class, allowing more time for hands-on skills training.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt; Students must score at least 70% and bring the completion certificate to class.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $0.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="7995" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC+SKILLS-PALS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;PALS Renew<span> </span> [AHA]&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Includes Online PALS HeartCode &amp; Skills Test Appointment&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $268.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="8405" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-SKILLS-PALS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;PALS Skills Session &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;(Student-provided Heartcode)&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $100.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="11304" style="box-sizing: border-box;">STB-OLT+SKILLS - &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;STOP THE BLEED® Skills testing - $22.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="7537" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-BBP - &lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/15-1405.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;Heartsaver® Bloodborne Pathogens Online&lt;br&gt;<span> </span> &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Learn to protect against exposure to blood or blood-containing materials. Pair with site-specific instruction to meet OSHA requirements for bloodborne pathogens.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;No in-person element to this course.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $23.32</option><span> </span>	<option value="8563" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-HS_FA - &lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1402.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;Heartsaver® First Aid Online&lt;br&gt;<span> </span> &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Teaches students the essential knowledge for providing basic first aid in various scenarios. Ideal for those seeking general first aid skills.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $18.50</option><span> </span>	<option value="7198" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ILT-BLS - &lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/ILT.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;BLS In-Person Instructor-led Renewal [AHA] &lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Add an in-person BLS renewal.<span> </span> Completed during PALS/ACLS/ASLS skills testing date/time.<span> </span> Receive a BLS certification card that matches your advanced cert's expiration date. &lt;b&gt;No online coursework required prior to class date.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $67.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="14570" style="box-sizing: border-box;">HSI-ILT-FACPRAED-USCG - &lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/HSINST-203.png" width="75" style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt; Are you taking this class to meet your USCG Captain's License &lt;i&gt;Elementary First Aid and CPR&lt;/i&gt; requirement?&lt;br&gt; &lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>Choose 'YES' for &lt;br&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>&lt;b&gt;"HSI Adult First Aid | CPR AED"&lt;/b&gt; (above),&lt;br&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>and check here to receive a &lt;b&gt;HSINST-203 Recognition of Participation&lt;/b&gt; document with your eCard. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $0.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="15084" style="box-sizing: border-box;">2025 ACLS INSTRUCTOR UPDATE - 2025 ACLS Instructor Update - $0.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="15081" style="box-sizing: border-box;">2025_BLS_INSTRUCTOR _UPDATE - 2025 BLS Instructor Update - $0.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="15082" style="box-sizing: border-box;">2025_HEARTSAVER_INSTRUCTOR_UPDATE - 2025 Heartsaver® Instructor Update - $0.00</option><span> </span>	<op