PALS Plus™: Sedation &amp; Analgesia Module&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;1.00 Hour Online, 0.25 Possible CE&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $22.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="11286" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-PALS+:TECH - A&lt;img src="https://d32pa7zymd21yl.cloudfront.net/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/8fce8601fc2f12d655469c75674153c0/2/0/20-1448_pals_plus_tech_dep_child.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS Plus™: Technology-Dependent Child Module&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;1.00 Hour Online, 0.25 Possible CE&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $22.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="11283" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-PALS+:ABUSE - A&lt;img src="https://d32pa7zymd21yl.cloudfront.net/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/8fce8601fc2f12d655469c75674153c0/2/0/20-1449_pals_plus_toxicology.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS Plus™: Child Abuse Module&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;1.00 Hour Online, 0.25 Possible CE&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $22.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="11457" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-PALS+:TRAUMA - A&lt;img src="https://d32pa7zymd21yl.cloudfront.net/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/8fce8601fc2f12d655469c75674153c0/2/0/20-1449_pals_plus_toxicology.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS Plus™: Trauma Module&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;1.00 Hour Online, 1.00 Possible CE&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $22.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="11282" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-PALS+:TOX - A&lt;img src="https://d32pa7zymd21yl.cloudfront.net/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/8fce8601fc2f12d655469c75674153c0/2/0/20-1450_pals_plus_child_absue.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS Plus™: Toxicology Module&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;1.00 Hour Online, 0.75 Possible CE&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $22.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="11284" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-PALS+:AIRWAY - A&lt;img src="https://d32pa7zymd21yl.cloudfront.net/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/8fce8601fc2f12d655469c75674153c0/2/0/20-1451_pals_plus_adv_airway.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS Plus™: Airway Management Module&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;1.00 Hour Online, 0.5 Possible CE&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $22.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="9668" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ILT-INSTR-ACLS - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/acls______.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;CLS - Instructor [American Heart Association] &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; - $300.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="14245" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ILT-INSTR-BLS - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/bls______.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;bLS - Instructor [American Heart Association] &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; - $300.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="11288" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-BP - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/15-1425.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Achieving Accuracy: BP Measurement eLearning Course&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Improve your blood pressure measurement skills with the new Achieving Accuracy: BP Measurement e-Learning module co-developed by the AHA and AMA.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt; - $26.50</option><span> </span>	<option value="7536" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-HS_CPRAED - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1401.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® CPR AED Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;eLearning portion of the Heartsaver CPR AED blended learning course, designed to teach students the cognitive information needed for CPR training and how to use an AED&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $30.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="7540" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-HS_FACPRAED-PEDI - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1404.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® Pediatric First Aid CPR AED Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;eLearning portion of the Heartsaver Pediatric First Aid CPR AED blended learning course, designed to teach students the cognitive information needed for pediatric first aid, CPR, and AED training&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $40.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="12055" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-INSTR-PALS-ESSENTIALS - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1417.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA PALS Instructor Essentials Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Self-directed, online portion of the PALS Instructor Essentials blended learning course covering the steps for becoming an AHA Instructor and steps of the instruction cycle&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/P&gt; - $41.20</option><span> </span>	<option value="8894" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-INSTR-HS-ESSENTIALS - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1418.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® Instructor Essentials Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Self-directed, online portion of the Heartsaver Instructor Essentials blended learning course covering steps for becoming an AHA Instructor and steps of the instruction cycle&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/P&gt; - $40.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="9660" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-INSTR-ACLS-ESSENTIALS - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1419.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA ACLS Instructor Essentials Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Self-directed, online portion of the ACLS Instructor Essentials blended learning Course covering steps for becoming an AHA ACLS Instructor and steps of the instruction cycle.&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/P&gt; - $40.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="7539" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-HS_FACPRAED-B - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1440.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® Basic - First Aid CPR AED Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Basic course focuses on core curriculum for providing first aid, CPR, and using an AED effectively. Covers basics of recognizing and administering first aid for common emergencies. &lt;b&gt;Not OSHA-compliant.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $40.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="11335" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-HS_FACPRAED-T - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1440.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® Total - First Aid CPR AED Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;eLearning portion of the Heartsaver Total® First Aid CPR AED course. Teaches the cognitive information needed for first aid, CPR, and AED training.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Completing all elements results in a course completion card designed to meet OSHA requirements.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $40.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="14049" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-HS_FACPRAED-T-95 - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-1440.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® Total - First Aid CPR AED Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;eLearning portion of the Heartsaver Total® First Aid CPR AED course. Teaches the cognitive information needed for first aid, CPR, and AED training.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Completing all elements results in a course completion card designed to meet OSHA requirements.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $95.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="7276" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-BLS - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-3553.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA BLS Provider HeartCode® &lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Use this option if you need a code for the online program.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $37.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="7864" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-ACLS - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/20-3554.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA HeartCode® ACLS Online&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Online portion of ACLS blended learning that will prepare students for hands-on skills session with an AHA ACLS Instructor or on a simulation station.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you have already been issued a HeartCode from your employer or school, select 'No' here.&lt;b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $185.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="9662" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ILT-ACLS - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/ILT.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;CLS In-person Instructor-led Renewal&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Builds on BLS skills, emphasizing high-quality CPR, emergency interventions, team dynamics, algorithms, post-cardiac-arrest care, airway management, and pharmacology. Add in-person ACLS renewal during PALS skills testing.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pre-test Reqired&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $225.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="8900" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ILT-HS_FA - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/ILT.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA Heartsaver® First Aid - $50.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="13620" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-ASLS/INHOSPITAL - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/In.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA ASLS Online: In-Hospital Provider&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Online portion of ASLS blended learning that will prepare students for hands-on skills session with an AHA Instructor.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you have already been issued a HeartCode from your employer or school, select 'No' here.&lt;b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $186.77</option><span> </span>	<option value="13619" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-ASLS/PREHOSPITAL - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/Pre.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA ASLS Online: Prehospital Provider&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Online portion of ASLS blended learning that will prepare students for hands-on skills session with an AHA Instructor.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you have already been issued a HeartCode from your employer or school, select 'No' here.&lt;b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $186.77</option><span> </span>	<option value="13621" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-ASLS/ALL - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/PreIn.jpg" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;HA ASLS Online: Prehospital &amp; In-Hospital Provider&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Online portion of ASLS blended learning that will prepare students for hands-on skills session with an AHA Instructor.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you have already been issued a HeartCode from your employer or school, select 'No' here.&lt;b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; - $185.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="8399" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ILT-HS_FACPRAED-USCG - A&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/JohnsHSFACPRAED.png" width="75"<span> </span> style="float:right; margin-left:10px;"&gt;re you taking this class to meet your USCG Captain's License &lt;i&gt;Elementary First Aid and CPR&lt;/i&gt; requirement?&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="color: #828282"&gt;&lt;br&gt;Choose 'YES' for&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;"Heartsaver® First Aid with CPR/AED - TOTAL"&lt;/b&gt; (above)&lt;br&gt;AND here to receive an AMERHA-216 with your eCard.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt; - $0.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="14233" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-ILT-INSTR-PALS - AHA - PALS - Become an American Heart Association Instructor &lt;div style="overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 5px;"&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/_AHA.png" alt="AHA Logo" style="width:25px; float:left; margin-right:5px;"&gt;<span> </span> <span> </span>&lt;img src="https://www.enrollware.com/sitefiles/coastalcprtraining/Class_Images/Ippin.png" alt="PALS Instructor Icon" style="float:right; width:100px; vertical-align:top;"&gt; &lt;/div&gt; - $300.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="15436" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-INSTR-BLS-ESSENTIALS - BLS Instructor Essentials Online - $40.00</option><span> </span>	<option value="12333" style="box-sizing: border-box;">AHA-HC-HS_FACPRAED-K12 -